A Hugo Site http://example.org/posts/2022-01-17-nuxt_%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%AD%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1/ -<p>在部署一个网站之后，我们最关心的事情无异于是访问量，以及对它的分析。国内的百度统计是一个不错的选择，基本的功能都是免费的。</p>
<!-- raw HTML omitted -->
<p>只需要在head中引入一串 javascript 代码即可。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">&lt;!-- &lt;script&gt;
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">var _hmt = _hmt || [];
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">(function() {
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">  var hm = document.createElement(&#34;script&#34;);
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">  hm.src = &#34;https://hm.baidu.com/hm.js?xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx&#34;;
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">  var s = document.getElementsByTagName(&#34;script&#34;)[0]; 
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">  s.parentNode.insertBefore(hm, s);
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">})();
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">&lt;/script&gt; --&gt;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>上面是百度提供的统计代码，需要放在 <code>&lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt;</code>中。</p>
<p>但是在nuxt中，没有传统的 <code>&lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt;</code> 。所以要对他进行一些处理。</p>
<h3 id="1-首先在根目录下-plugins-新建一个文件-baidujs">1. 首先在根目录下 <code>/plugins</code> 新建一个文件 <code>baidu.js</code></h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-js" data-lang="js"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22">// /plugins/baidu.js
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22"></span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">export</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">default</span> ({app: {router}, store}) =&gt; {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  <span style="color:#228b22">/* 每次路由变更时进行pv统计 */</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  router.afterEach((to, from) =&gt; {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#228b22">/* 告诉增加一个PV */</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">try</span> {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#658b00">window</span>._hmt = <span style="color:#658b00">window</span>._hmt || []
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#658b00">window</span>._hmt.push([<span style="color:#cd5555">&#39;_trackPageview&#39;</span>, to.fullPath])
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    } <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">catch</span> (e) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  })
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>}
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="2-配置-nuxtconfigjs-文件">2. 配置 nuxt.config.js 文件</h3>
<ol>
<li>在 <code>plugins</code>中：</li>
</ol>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-js" data-lang="js"><span style="display:flex;"><span>plugins: [
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    src: <span style="color:#cd5555">&#39;~/plugins/baidu&#39;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>],
</span></span></code></pre></div><ol start="2">
<li>在 <code>head</code>中：</li>
</ol>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-js" data-lang="js"><span style="display:flex;"><span>head: {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  <span style="color:#228b22">// ...
