</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    { src: <span style="color:#cd5555">&#39;https://hm.baidu.com/hm.js?xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx&#39;</span> }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  ]
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>},
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>在script中写入百度统计提供的 url 即可，按照对应的字符。</p>
